meanings.definition: A plural form of the surname ZIMMI.
meanings.english_definition: Plural form of the surname Zimmi.

examples.sentence: The Zimmis family has a long history in the town.
examples.translation: ジミ家はこの町で長い歴史を持っています。

usage_notes.explanation: This entry refers to the plural form of a surname. It is used when referring to multiple members of the Zimmi family or multiple instances of something associated with the Zimmi family.

readability_explanation.text: This entry is for the plural form of a surname, so its readability is dependent on familiarity with the name itself.
